window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When miserly millionaire Barnaby Galen is found dead in his dilapidated mansion, two corpses are on the scene - the murder victim and the murder weapon. Staring into the skeleton face of a horror prop called Granny, Galen dies of fright, leaving only enemies and suspects behind. With echoes of Scrooge and the Ghost of Christmas Yet to Come,<i> Blue Christmas</i> is a witty, heartfelt romantic mystery that will make fans of Emma Jameson's best-selling series want to stand up and cheer.</p> <p>The Lord &amp; Lady Hetheridge Mystery Series (ongoing)</p> <ol> <li><i>Ice Blue</i></li> <li><i>Blue Murder</i></li> <li><i>Something Blue</i></li> <li><i>Black &amp; Blue</i></li> <li><i>Blue Blooded</i></li> <li><i>Blue Christmas</i></li> </ol>"; 
